author: Reuters Editorial
title: Beneficial Bancorp Inc Announces Q1 Earnings Per Share $0.13
text:
April 20, 2018 / 11:35 AM / Updated 18 minutes ago BRIEF-Beneficial Bancorp Inc Announces Q1 Earnings Per Share $0.13 Reuters Staff 
April 20 (Reuters) - Beneficial Bancorp Inc: 
* BENEFICIAL BANCORP, INC. ANNOUNCES FIRST QUARTER RESULTS AND CASH DIVIDEND TO SHAREHOLDERS * Q1 EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.13 
* Q1 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.13 â€” THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S * SETS QUARTERLY CASH DIVIDEND OF $0.06PER SHARE 
* FOR QUARTER ENDED MARCH 31, 2018, NET INTEREST INCOME WAS $43.2 MILLION, AN INCREASE 6.0%, FROM QUARTER ENDED MARCH 31, 2017 
* NET INTEREST INCOME INCREASED $2.4 MILLION, OR 6.0%, FOR QUARTER COMPARED TO SAME PERIOD IN PRIOR YEAR Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Reuters.Briefs@thomsonreuters.com)
